com.karmant.syn

Class SynResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.karmant.syn.SynResult

  • public class SynResult
extends java.lang.Object
    The result returned by a SynParser. Contains an Abstract Syntax Tree and some statistics information, such as total line and character count.
